title: When do we get our Ocean Week rewards?
body: Was wondering when we'd get them.

replies.body: Most rewards will be rolled out during this patch cycle! For more information about the Ocean Week rewards, check out the [**Oceania is Victorious**](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/community/community-events/oceania-victorious) announcement for Ocean Week!

yes, i know that. but i was wondering on a specific date, we already got the summoner icon, was wondering about free 
champ
It's being distributed as we speak and will hopefully be completely be distributed by the end of the week.
